snippet.title: Game & Watch - Popeye (Panorama Screen) (c)1983 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description:
With the emulation of Popeye all of the Tabletop / Panorama Game & Watch units have been emulated (except minor variations such as the Cement Factory with the 'Another One Bites The Dust' music removed)  Thanks as usual, to Algestam for this one and to DarthMarino for the artwork, as well as MooglyGuy for contributing the unit that was dumped.

Artwork can be found at https://drive.google.com/drive/u/1/folders/1vl9O-0jIGCHHY_lrWpOwBtqTXEKsVGOY?usp=sharing
